{
  "info": {
    "name": "School Management System API",
    "_postman_id": "sms-api-collection-0001",
    "description": "Full API collection for the School Management System (backend at http://localhost:8000/api).\n\nAuth is COOKIE-BASED (httpOnly). Usage:\n1. Run 'Auth > Login (SuperAdmin)' first — the server returns a Set-Cookie 'token' which Postman stores in its cookie jar and sends automatically on every subsequent request. No Authorization header is needed.\n2. Make sure Postman's cookie jar is enabled (Settings > General > 'Automatically follow redirects' off is fine; cookies are on by default). Cookies are stored for the 'localhost' domain.\n3. To switch users, run another Login request (it overwrites the cookie). Run 'Logout' to clear it.\n4. Fill the id variables (studentId, classId, subjectId, yearId, etc.) under the collection's Variables tab as you create records, or let the capture scripts set them from responses.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:8000/api" },
    { "key": "token", "value": "" },
    { "key": "studentId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "teacherId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "classId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "sectionId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "subjectId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "yearId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "feeId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "paymentId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "reportCardId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "attendanceId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "notificationId", "value": "" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth & Permissions",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login (SuperAdmin)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const data = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (data && data.token) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('token', data.token);",
                  "  console.log('Token saved to {{token}}');",
                  "}",
                  "if (data && data.user && data.user._id) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('currentUserId', data.user._id);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"identifier\": \"superadmin@school.com\",\n  \"password\": \"superadmin\"\n}" },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["auth", "login"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (Admin)",
          "event": [
            { "listen": "test", "script": { "type": "text/javascript", "exec": ["const d = pm.response.json(); if (d.token) pm.collectionVariables.set('token', d.token);"] } }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"identifier\": \"admin@school.com\",\n  \"password\": \"admin\"\n}" },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["auth", "login"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (Cashier)",
          "event": [
            { "listen": "test", "script": { "type": "text/javascript", "exec": ["const d = pm.response.json(); if (d.token) pm.collectionVariables.set('token', d.token);"] } }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
